<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="9">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xi-xi-89-63" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xi-xi-89-63" class="zg-link" title="西西">西西</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ray-wang-44-91" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ray-wang-44-91" class="zg-link" title="Ray Wang">Ray Wang</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-lei-29-89" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-lei-29-89" class="zg-link" title="张磊">张磊</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="709664" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>容易被催眠的人需要满足一下条件：<br><br>1.非低智商。<br><br>2.高情商。<br><br>3.想象力丰富。<br><br>4.懂得专注。<br><br>5.容易相信别人。<br><br>6.多愁善感。</p><p>满足以上条件，无论你是催眠师，厨师，劳改犯，变态杀人狂，老师，米粉，魅友，果粉，狱头，司机，搬砖工人，妓女，嫖客都可进入催眠。</p>


</div>

</div>
</div>
